{"tid":94832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曹星如連勝20場 :0(","createTime":"2017-01-25T13:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T06:14:09.000Z","uid":70677,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81f64a64697faf1ea18de4c4744f2a2dd1c09225","tid":94832,"uid":70677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"依度有4大拳擊組織嘅世界排名榜.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fightnews.com/rankings-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fightnews.com%2Frankings-2&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=40a5f82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fightnews.com/rankings-2</a><br />\n每個組織都有自已嘅排名. 表列每個組織排頭嗰15個拳手嘅名, 咁即係有權話自己係Super Flyweight/Jr. Bantamweight (115 lbs)世界排名15名以内嘅拳手都有五十幾, 六十人.<br />\n大家不妨估吓曹星如過去20場嘅對手究竟喺世界排名第幾?<br />\n答案係..........唔好意思, 無一個對手有排名. 😂<br />\n咁家吓曹星如在WBO超蠅量級拳手排名己經躍升至世界第一, 咁佢下一場比賽對手會唔會勁d?<br />\n答案係..........唔好意思, 下一場比賽對手向井寬史一樣係無排名. 😂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170122/56206936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170122%2F56206936&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6cca4f38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsports%2F20170122%2F56206936&h=848194b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/sports/20170122/56206936</a>"},{"pid":"b13b84ca2ceb1a7834b9a4739fd567c9adb689d9","tid":94832,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"最近多左人知道佢擦數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fdc75187669c46874c348ac7d58c4a42666669e","tid":94832,"uid":70677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近多左人知道佢擦數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/214138_74b23be341a991235b2db265b5292568.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F214138_74b23be341a991235b2db265b5292568.jpg&h=dbbec3ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed779cdcb385c1d02246a1cf60125d5dba68d837","tid":94832,"uid":70677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"《一場未赢过!成日被打到抛白毛巾投降!世界排名二十名以外!自封亞泰區拳王的向井寬史!和曹星如爭奪三條金腰帶》<br />\n首先看看曹星如今次對手向井寬史 (Hirofumi Mukai) 嘅世界排名.<br />\n4大拳擊組織都有自己的世界排名榜, 但向井寬史都入唔到這些組織頭嗰15名<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fightnews.com/rankings-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fightnews.com%2Frankings-2&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=40a5f82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fightnews.com/rankings-2</a><br />\n其實在WBC, 向井寬史係排名#38.  在IBF, 佢係排名#19<br />\n<a href=\"http://wbcboxing.com/wbceng/ratings?layout=edit&amp;id=154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwbcboxing.com%2Fwbceng%2Fratings%3Flayout%3Dedit%26id%3D154&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e830df58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wbcboxing.com/wbceng/ratings?layout=edit&amp;id=154</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iboboxing.com/rankings/115.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iboboxing.com%2Frankings%2F115.html&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=25344c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.iboboxing.com/rankings/115.html</a><br />\n<br />\n再看看向井寬史嘅賽事記錄<br />\n<a href=\"http://boxrec.com/boxer/506772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fboxrec.com%2Fboxer%2F506772&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e2ae216f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://boxrec.com/boxer/506772</a><br />\n<br />\n這是向井寬史在15/11/2013對 Srisaket Sor Rungvisai 的比賽片段.  Srisaket Sor Rungvisai 在 WBC Super Flyweight 排名#2.  最後向井寬史被打到要扔毛巾投降.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51GW6IJ1bMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D51GW6IJ1bMM&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=fe368319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=51GW6IJ1bMM</a><br />\n<br />\n在2015至2016年, 向井寬史打咗5場.  其中4場嘅對手同佢一樣, 在4大拳擊組織中, 世界頭嗰15名都無佢地份.  <br />\n只有在16/9/2015那場比賽, 向井寬史對返一個在 Bantamweight 有排名嘅大森将平(Shohei Omori) ( WBC#7, IBF#14, WBO#11).  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3oPFJtTm24I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3oPFJtTm24I&d=WR7F0vbvcweQvB3cyi14pnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=984f5cfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3oPFJtTm24I</a> <br />\n比賽片段在1:39開始.  結果向井寬史再次被打到要扔毛巾投降(片段在2:08)<br />\n<br />\n見到d宣傳叫向井寬史做WBO亞太區&rdquo;拳王&rdquo;, 又話依場比賽係爭奪三條金腰帶, 都唔知好嬲定好笑.  為咗完成21連勝, 走去揾個咁嘅&rdquo;扔毛巾拳王&rdquo;做對手.  大家仲以為好威, 因為香港出咗個所謂&rdquo;世界拳王&rdquo;. 其實係比人笑到面黄. 😂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/214322_3d5c917cdec93485534015ae5ec295a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F214322_3d5c917cdec93485534015ae5ec295a4.jpg&h=10e8d748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L58R680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL58R680.jpg&h=639a6bef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e5dbecafdd8f55ec8f88c415420b945400b981f","tid":94832,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"刷下經又有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b00d2a69f45bd9538f7b77f6c6f62d51d352ea1","tid":94832,"uid":57049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"其實想知行內人係點睇佢"},{"pid":"748bb321b8da3318af371312b2d6b1af56f495d7","tid":94832,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:05:12